<!--blog entry-->
<h2 style="background-color:rgb(157,255,176); font-family:Calibri; border:white; border-width:5px; border-style:double; text-align:left">Move In Day</h2>
<small><i><p>3/20/2022</p></i></small>
<pre>
	After a hard decision to move away from my home,
	I have finally packed all my stuff and moved to a
	new island. Of what I've seen so far, I think I am
	going to love it here!

	First of all, there are so many apple trees. It's a
	nice change from the pear trees back home. Everybody
	here is also so nice, especially Isabelle. Although I
	feel that one racoon asks for way too much money from me.
</pre>
<i><q>nutty</q></i>
<br><br>

